{
  "stem": "22944.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when Pernik came back, Pernik came back a few hours later and told us that the German was convinced there aren't Jews in this place and the miraculous escape of not entering into our apartment, he himself was quite surprised what happened.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were tremendously relieved, obviously, but we never knew what was next going to happen, obviously.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was always touch and go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] On a number of occasions, there was-- the neighbors were suspicious.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not the next door, but the other neighbors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we carried on staying there for, uh-- till the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to go down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every time when some news came about, that this was only the biggest incidence of them suspecting us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there were other incidents of suspecting Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then we found out there was another-- one or two other people hiding in the mill, by somebody else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That, we found out after the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the news came, of course, that gradually that the Russian soldiers are getting nearer to our area.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we taken down again to the cellar.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Again-- this time, we were taken down to the cellar for a different reason.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because there was a rumor that the Russian army are approaching, and the German [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] army are getting panicky.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They really did not know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we were put down in the cellar, so that-- just to save ourselves from the shooting.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, at this time, there were plane coming-- bombing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The army was coming now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, it was a different kind of problem.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
